|---|---|---|---|
| Brightness (CSS) | sRGB | `in × amount` | none |
| Brightness (offset) | RGB | `in + b` | none |
| Brightness (GIMP) | RGB | piecewise | none |
| Contrast (CSS) | sRGB | `(in−0.5)×c + 0.5` | none |
| Contrast (GIMP) | RGB | `(in−0.5)×tan(…) + 0.5` | none |
| Contrast (PIL) | RGB | `mean + f×(in−mean)` | none |
| Saturation (CSS) | RGB matrix | 3×3 luma matrix | none |
| Saturation (shader) | RGB+luma | `mix(grey, color, s)` | none |
| Saturation (true) | HSL/HSV | scale S channel | **YES** |
| Hue rotate (CSS) | RGB matrix | cos/sin 3×3 | none |
| Hue rotate (true) | HSV | `rgb2hsv + Δh → hsv2rgb` | **YES** |
| Temperature (raw) | Camera linear RGB | per-channel gain | normalization |
| Temperature (shader) | YIQ + overlay | Q-shift + warm blend | none |
| Tint | YIQ Q / LAB a* / CIE UCS | Q-channel shift | none |
| Shadows / Highlights | RGB + luma mask | Gaussian/smoothstep × ratio | **YES** (lum=0) |

